uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor.match

Class DCustomMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor.match.DCustomMatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMatcher

    public class DCustomMatcher
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMatcher
    Implementation of the IMatcher interface that enables customisation of the matching mechanisms provided by a "core-matcher", based on a particular domain-specific Object Model (OM). The core-matcher can be provided by any implementation of IMatcher.

    Specific customisations to the basic matching mechanisms are provided in the form of appropriate extensions of the DMatcherCustomiser class, which form an ordered list, and whose pre- and post-processing methods will be applied in the relevant order before and after each matching operation.
